title: Random spider-verse headcanons/scenarios
body:
because i was bored

  • Since I noticed how Noir had the Rubik’s cube in his coat since probably the first time we saw him with it, I keep imagining that he keeps a bunch of other stuff in there like his glasses, a pen, a newspaper, spare change, a paper clip, and whatever is in a character’s pockets when they’re shaken upside down.
  • That being said, Spider-Ham probably has even more in his pockets. Things that one wouldn’t normally be able to fit in a pocket, like an anvil, an anchor, a toaster, etc.
  • Noir would want to teach Peni how to box in order for her to better defend herself. She’s unsure about it at first, but he keeps coaxing her to give him her best shot. One he says “pretend I just hurt your robot”, she goes yandere for a split second and socks him in the stomach to the ground. He’d be very proud of her.
  • Miles would try the shoulder touch on Gwen now that they know each other more, but he wouldn’t succeed without the both of them cracking up once he tries the “hey” part.
  • Also every time I listen to Hello by Lionel Richie I can’t stop thinking of how much Peter B. would probably love to listen to it when depressed

summary: You ever think about how Peter Parker, who had a mom and sad who loved him with all their hearts because he was their whole...
body:
You ever think about how Peter Parker, who had a mom and sad who loved him with all their hearts because he was their whole world, and an Aunt and Uncle who loved their nephew because they couldn’t have children. Then one day his parents drop him off with his aunt and uncle to go on a trip for work.

And they die in a plane crash.

And peter is so young he can’t even remember them? And how he grew up for years thinking Ben and May where his mom and dad only to learn what he’s lost? And how despite that they both give him all the love they can give because Peter is their son now?

And how because of one thing Peter didn’t do, that neither May or Ben would ever blame him for, his uncle died and feels guilty about it?

Cuz I do.

And then I think of how Peter wishes that any of them could have met MJ because she brings so much joy into his life.

summary: The new car from home posters are so badly designed marvel has so much money but can’t afford a graphic designer with taste
question: The new car from home posters are so badly designed marvel has so much money but can’t afford a graphic designer with taste
answer:
Hmmm I gotta say, they’re not “bad” posters…. but they’re 🅱️ORING as hell!! I understand that they’re trying to market themselves using the heavy-hitting actors in static positions but… ://

I know they’re putting out /easy/ & digestible content to reach a wider audience but it’s incredibly lackluster for the fans. There’s so many ways to put out a creative and playful campaign for this…… but u know… the easy $$$ . Though I will say, so far, a lot of the media in spiderman: homecoming HAS been really cool and creative (I.e. the end credits) so I do trust that we’ll see some cool things soon .
